```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as User
  participant D as Route53/DNS
  participant A as Region A (ALB/Service)
  participant B as Region B (ALB/Service)
  participant H as Health Checks

  U->>D: Resolve service.example.com
  D-->>U: Region A endpoint (lowest latency + healthy)
  U->>A: Request
  A-->>U: Response

  Note over A,H: Region A outage occurs
  H->>D: Mark Region A unhealthy
  U->>D: Resolve again (TTL)
  D-->>U: Region B endpoint
  U->>B: Request
  B-->>U: Response
```
